---
import DemoLayout from '../../layouts/DemoLayout.astro';

const title = "AI Resume Screener Platform Demo — YongAI";
const description = "Experience YongAI's enterprise AI recruiting platform. AI screening saves 10+ hours per open role — average cost per hire is $4,700 (SHRM, 2023).";
---

<DemoLayout title={title} description={description} demoType="resume-screener">
  <!-- Stats Bar -->
  <div class="py-4 bg-bg-raised border-b border-[rgba(0,0,0,0.06)] mt-18">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
        <div>
          <span class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black text-warning">7 sec</span>
          <div class="text-sm text-text-muted">Initial Resume Scan (Ladders Inc., 2018)</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black text-success">10+ hrs</span>
          <div class="text-sm text-text-muted">Saved per Open Role</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black text-info">$4,700</span>
          <div class="text-sm text-text-muted">Average Cost per Hire (SHRM, 2023)</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black text-purple-400">2 hrs</span>
          <div class="text-sm text-text-muted">AI vs 5 Days Manual</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-20 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <p class="section-label mb-4">CANDIDATE SCREENING</p>
      <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-black mb-6 leading-none text-[#1C1C1E]">
        Your team spends 10 hours screening resumes per open role. <br class="hidden lg:block"/><span class="text-[#C2410C]">AI gets it done in 2 hours.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-text-muted max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        Most of that time is wasted on candidates who don't qualify. AI reads every resume, scores each one against your requirements, and hands you a ranked shortlist in 2 hours instead of 5 days.
      </p>
      <p class="text-base text-text-faint mb-8 font-medium">↓ Paste a job description below to see it screen candidates</p>
      <!-- Hero Illustration -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-8 px-4">
        <img
          src="/illustrations/hero-resume-screener.svg"
          alt="Resume Screener illustration"
          class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-2xl shadow-black/50 border border-[rgba(0,0,0,0.08)]"
          loading="eager"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Engagement Context Banner -->
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 mb-16">
    <div class="bg-[rgba(194,65,12,0.05)] border border-[rgba(194,65,12,0.15)] rounded-2xl p-6">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-start gap-6">
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#C2410C] mb-1">EXAMPLE ENGAGEMENT</p>
          <p class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1C1C1E]">A recruiting agency like yours</p>
          <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">20–50 recruiters · Talent acquisition · 6-week engagement</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-text-faint mb-1">WHAT WE TYPICALLY FIND</p>
          <p class="text-[#1C1C1E] font-medium">Recruiters spending 50+ hours per open role on manual screening — 80% of that time on candidates who won't make it past the first round</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-text-faint mb-1">WHAT THIS DEMO SHOWS</p>
          <p class="text-[#1C1C1E] font-medium">The screening system we'd build as a Week 3 deliverable</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- How We Got Here -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-[#F4F3EF] border-t border-[rgba(0,0,0,0.06)]">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="section-label mb-2 text-center">HOW A YONGAI ENGAGEMENT WORKS</p>
      <p class="text-center text-text-muted mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Before we build anything, we spend two weeks understanding how your agency actually operates. This demo is what Week 3 looks like.</p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[rgba(194,65,12,0.1)] text-[#C2410C] font-black flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-sm">1</div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-[#1C1C1E] mb-1">Week 1–2: Discovery</p>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Stakeholder interviews with recruiters, account managers, and operations. We shadow the screening process across active roles to understand real workflow patterns.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[rgba(194,65,12,0.1)] text-[#C2410C] font-black flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-sm">2</div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-[#1C1C1E] mb-1">Week 2–3: Analysis</p>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">We identify where time is lost and revenue leaks. In most agencies, manual screening is the first target — recruiters doing expensive filtering work that AI does in seconds.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 opacity-100">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[rgba(194,65,12,0.2)] text-[#C2410C] font-black flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 ring-2 ring-[#C2410C] text-sm">3</div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-[#1C1C1E] mb-1">Week 3: This deliverable ←</p>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">AI screening system integrated with your ATS. Reads every resume, scores against requirements, and delivers a ranked shortlist in hours instead of days.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center mt-8">
        <a href="/demos/workflow-audit" class="text-[#C2410C] text-sm font-semibold hover:underline">← See the full process audit that started this engagement</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Job Input Section -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="glassmorphism rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-12">
        <div class="text-center mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-[#1C1C1E]">Step 1: What are you hiring for?</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-text-muted">Paste your job description to see how AI finds candidates that match what you're looking for</p>
        </div>
        
        <textarea 
          class="w-full h-48 bg-bg-raised border border-border-light rounded-xl p-6 text-text-primary placeholder:text-text-faint focus:border-success focus:ring-2 focus:ring-success/20 focus:outline-none resize-vertical font-mono text-sm"
          id="job-description"
          placeholder="Paste your job description here...

We are seeking a Senior Software Engineer with 5+ years of experience in full-stack development. Must have strong expertise in React, Node.js, and cloud platforms (AWS/Azure). Experience with microservices architecture and team leadership preferred. Bachelor's degree in Computer Science or equivalent experience required."
        ></textarea>
        
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-6 mb-8">
          <button class="px-4 py-2 bg-bg-raised border border-border-light rounded-lg text-sm text-text-muted hover:text-text-primary hover:border-success transition-all duration-200" onclick="loadSampleJob('software')">
            Software Engineer
          </button>
          <button class="px-4 py-2 bg-bg-raised border border-border-light rounded-lg text-sm text-text-muted hover:text-text-primary hover:border-success transition-all duration-200" onclick="loadSampleJob('marketing')">
            Marketing Manager
          </button>
          <button class="px-4 py-2 bg-bg-raised border border-border-light rounded-lg text-sm text-text-muted hover:text-text-primary hover:border-success transition-all duration-200" onclick="loadSampleJob('sales')">
            Sales Director
          </button>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center">
          <button 
            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-success to-yong-green text-white px-12 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-success/25"
            onclick="analyzeJob()"
          >
            Analyze Candidates
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Candidates Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-[#F4F3EF] border-t border-[rgba(0,0,0,0.06)]" id="candidates-section" style="display: none;">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <p class="section-label mb-4 text-center">YOUR SHORTLIST</p>
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-[#1C1C1E]">Here are your top candidates — ranked and explained.</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-text-muted max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Our AI automatically scores and ranks candidates based on how well they match your job needs. Click any candidate to see detailed breakdown.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12" id="candidates-grid">
        <!-- Candidates will be populated here -->
      </div>
      
      <!-- Detailed Analysis Panel -->
      <div class="hidden lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mt-12 slide-in-up" id="detailed-analysis" style="display: none;">
        <div class="glassmorphism rounded-2xl p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-xl font-bold mb-6">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-success">
              <polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"></polyline>
            </svg>
            Skills & Experience Analysis
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4" id="skills-detailed">
            <!-- Skills will be populated here -->
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="glassmorphism rounded-2xl p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-xl font-bold mb-6">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-info">
              <path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"></path>
            </svg>
            Cultural Fit & Soft Skills
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4" id="cultural-fit">
            <!-- Cultural fit metrics will be populated here -->
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-success/10 border border-success/20 rounded-xl p-6 mt-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-3">✓</div>
            <div class="font-semibold text-success mb-2">Bias-Free Analysis</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-text-muted">AI removes unconscious bias based on names, schools, or demographics</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ROI Calculator -->
  <section class="py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <p class="section-label mb-4">THE ECONOMICS</p>
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 text-[#1C1C1E]">What does 10 hours per role actually cost you?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-text-muted">Put in your numbers. The calculator uses your real volume.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="glassmorphism rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-12">
        <div class="text-center mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">ROI Calculator</h3>
          <p class="text-text-muted">Input your current numbers to see projected savings</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
          <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-text-muted mb-2">Resumes per Month</label>
            <input type="number" class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-bg-raised border border-border-light rounded-xl text-text-primary focus:border-success focus:ring-2 focus:ring-success/20 focus:outline-none" id="resumes-month" value="800" oninput="calculateROI()">
          </div>
          <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-text-muted mb-2">Avg. Recruiter Hourly Rate ($)</label>
            <input type="number" class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-bg-raised border border-border-light rounded-xl text-text-primary focus:border-success focus:ring-2 focus:ring-success/20 focus:outline-none" id="hourly-rate" value="35" oninput="calculateROI()">
          </div>
          <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-text-muted mb-2">Minutes per Resume (Current)</label>
            <input type="number" class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-bg-raised border border-border-light rounded-xl text-text-primary focus:border-success focus:ring-2 focus:ring-success/20 focus:outline-none" id="time-per-resume" value="15" oninput="calculateROI()">
          </div>
          <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-text-muted mb-2">Team Size</label>
            <input type="number" class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-bg-raised border border-border-light rounded-xl text-text-primary focus:border-success focus:ring-2 focus:ring-success/20 focus:outline-none" id="team-size" value="8" oninput="calculateROI()">
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">
          <div class="glassmorphism rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-success mb-2" id="monthly-savings">$9,000</div>
            <div class="text-text-muted">Monthly Savings</div>
          </div>
          <div class="glassmorphism rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-info mb-2" id="annual-savings">$108,000</div>
            <div class="text-text-muted">Annual Savings</div>
          </div>
          <div class="glassmorphism rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-warning mb-2" id="payback-period">2.1</div>
            <div class="text-text-muted">Payback (Months)</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-info/5 border border-info/20 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <p class="font-semibold">Projections based on SHRM and industry research.</p>
          <p class="text-text-muted">Actual results vary by implementation. Typical time savings: 10+ hours per open role.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ATS Integration -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-bg-raised border-t border-[rgba(0,0,0,0.06)]">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <p class="section-label mb-4">FITS YOUR EXISTING STACK</p>
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 text-[#1C1C1E]">Ranked shortlist goes straight into your ATS.</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-text-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">No new system to learn. AI screens in the background and pushes the ranked shortlist to Bullhorn, Greenhouse, Lever, or wherever you already work.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto glassmorphism rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 border-b border-[rgba(0,0,0,0.06)] bg-bg-raised">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-success">
              <rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="9"></rect>
              <rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="5"></rect>
              <rect x="14" y="12" width="7" height="9"></rect>
              <rect x="3" y="16" width="7" height="5"></rect>
            </svg>
            <span class="font-semibold">Bullhorn Integration</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-success">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-success rounded-full"></div>
            Connected
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="p-8">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-success/10 flex items-center justify-center text-success text-2xl mx-auto mb-4">•</div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Auto-Sync</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">New candidates automatically pulled from your recruiting system</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-info/10 flex items-center justify-center text-info text-2xl mx-auto mb-4">•</div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">AI Analysis</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Resume analyzed & scored in under 30 seconds</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-warning/10 flex items-center justify-center text-warning text-2xl mx-auto mb-4">•</div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Smart Ranking</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Candidates ranked by fit score with insights</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-purple-400/10 flex items-center justify-center text-purple-400 text-2xl mx-auto mb-4">•</div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Push Back</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Results & notes synced back to your recruiting system</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Before/After Comparison -->
  <section class="py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <p class="section-label mb-4 text-center">BEFORE VS. AFTER</p>
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-[#1C1C1E]">5 days of manual screening vs. 2 hours with AI.</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-text-muted">See the dramatic difference AI makes to your screening process</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div class="glassmorphism rounded-2xl p-8 border-l-4 border-l-danger">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-danger/20 text-danger text-sm font-semibold rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">Before</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Manual Screening</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-text-muted mb-6">The old way of doing things</p>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-bg-raised rounded-xl">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-danger text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">1</div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold">Download & Read Resume</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-text-muted">3-4 minutes per resume</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-bg-raised rounded-xl">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-danger text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">2</div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold">Manual Skill Extraction</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-text-muted">5-7 minutes per resume</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-bg-raised rounded-xl">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-danger text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">3</div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold">Compare Against Job Requirements</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-text-muted">3-5 minutes per resume</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-bg-raised rounded-xl">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-danger text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">4</div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold">Write Notes & Score</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-text-muted">2-3 minutes per resume</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-bg-raised rounded-xl">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-danger text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">5</div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold">Prepare Interview Questions</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-text-muted">5-8 minutes per candidate</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-[rgba(0,0,0,0.06)]">
            <div class="text-4xl font-black text-danger mb-2">15-20 min</div>
            <div class="text-text-muted">per resume</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="glassmorphism rounded-2xl p-8 border-l-4 border-l-success">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-success/20 text-success text-sm font-semibold rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">After</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">AI-Powered Screening</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-text-muted mb-6">The YongAI way</p>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-bg-raised rounded-xl">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-success text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">1</div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold">Automatic Resume Parsing</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-text-muted">5 seconds per resume</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-bg-raised rounded-xl">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-success text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">2</div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold">AI Skill & Experience Extraction</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-text-muted">10 seconds per resume</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-bg-raised rounded-xl">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-success text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">3</div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold">Intelligent Job Matching</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-text-muted">5 seconds per resume</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-bg-raised rounded-xl">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-success text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">4</div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold">Automated Scoring & Notes</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-text-muted">5 seconds per resume</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-bg-raised rounded-xl">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-success text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">5</div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold">Custom Interview Question Generation</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-text-muted">5 seconds per candidate</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-[rgba(0,0,0,0.06)]">
            <div class="text-4xl font-black text-success mb-2">30 sec</div>
            <div class="text-text-muted">per resume</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-[#F4F3EF] border-t border-[rgba(0,0,0,0.06)]">
